{"tid":953402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SpaceX火箭將美軍第三代GPS定位系統衛星送上軌道","createTime":"2018-12-24T02:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T05:38:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"530242c04442e9926dc834a2bbf6655eb08b1d04","tid":953402,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1434739_1_L_20181224010540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1434739_1_L_20181224010540.jpg&h=5b80810f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獵鷹9號運載火箭攜帶美軍第三代大型定位系統衛星，發射到軌道上。（美聯社資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國太空探索技術公司SpaceX的獵鷹9號運載火箭，攜帶美軍第三代大型定位系統衛星升空，並順利將衛星送上軌道。<br />\n<br />\n衛星重3.8噸，是美軍第一顆進入軌道的第三代大型定位衛星。根據計劃，將有另外31顆同類衛星被送上軌道，逐步取代現有的定位衛星，確保全球定位訊號繼續運作。<br />\n<br />\n運載火箭原定在上星期二升空，但在起飛前7分鐘，火箭第一階段感應器有異常，發射被取消。發射場的天氣情況其後轉差，令火箭延至當地星期日才升空。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434739-20181224.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434739-20181224.htm&d=shPZLtxq8zKrM9oTtNKLMUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c0de513a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434739-20181224.htm&h=d4a45930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434739-20181224.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2732729ffba8d7161b48d3f923f34d1091c451d1","tid":953402,"uid":130879,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:24:53.000Z","msg":"收唔收得番支火箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fae6b3a7e9fa4e33efc9c9bb4340f3294b5ec5","tid":953402,"uid":83623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2732729ffba8d7161b48d3f923f34d1091c451d1","tid":953402,"uid":130879,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:24:53.000Z","msg":"收唔收得番支火箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" c